    <Note Title="Topic" Type="Summary" Ordinal="1" xml:lang="en">Security update for libidn</Note>
    <Note Title="Details" Type="General" Ordinal="2" xml:lang="en">libidn was updated to version 1.31 to fix one security issue.

This security issue was fixed:
- CVE-2015-2059: Out-of-bounds read with stringprep on invalid UTF-8 (bsc#923241).
